ashtottari_dasha.reasons: Rahu not in Kendra from Lagna/Moon  Ashtottari not applicable; use Vimshottari.

chara_dasha_jaimini.antar_rule: Antar orientation by explicit sign list (1,5,6,7,11,12 -> DIRECT); antar start: direct->second forward, reverse->previous; Mah counting: start excluded end included; same-sign->12; equal split among 12 antars; final antar clipped to MD end
